description:
What exactly is grace, and how does it connect to the law that God has given us? Why is there so much conflict among Christians concerning the law?

This #cut from the video, “The Sabbath [Why Does it Matter?]”
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=99NG34oMsxE&t=925s, explains how salvation comes through grace instead of the law. The law has been given to humanity because of God’s grace and His desire to restore us to His image. It is a reflection of His love for humanity.
